{
  "chapter": 15,
  "chapter_summary": "本章《第十五回 神龙摆尾》以“陆冠英扶起完颜康，见他给点中了穴道，动弹不得，只两颗眼珠光溜溜的转动。”开篇，围绕主要人物的行踪、冲突和江湖牵连展开。中段写到“旁人扮不到那么像。\"郭靖心下佩服，道：\"你瞧得真仔细。”，推动人物关系和武功线索变化；后段转向“这一招是他在危急之中胡乱打出，全无章法理路可言。”，并以“郭靖陪着黄蓉，一起将程大小姐送回。程大小姐悄悄将闺名对黄蓉说了，原来名叫程瑶迦。”收束，为后续章节继续埋下因果。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆乘风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我答应过你师父，放了你去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_cong",
      "speaker_name": "朱聪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位是什么官儿，你也带了走罢。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "段天德",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "段天德道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_tian_de",
      "speaker_name": "段天德",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "段天德道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_tian_de",
      "speaker_name": "段天德",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他刚才听得陆乘风说陆冠英是枯木大师弟子，又向陆冠英说道：",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "陆乘风道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "烦借纸笔一用。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "二师父，请你书写先父的灵位。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭义士啸天之灵位",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖喝道：",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "段天德道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "完颜康惊道：",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "瞥眼见到郭靖脸色铁青，丝毫不为自己言语所动，当即跪倒，在郭啸天灵前连连叩头，叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你待怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖大喜，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨康道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "柯镇恶道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱聪等人均表赞同。郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_xiao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "韩小莹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "桃花岛之约，不必去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "弟子倘若不去，岂不失信于他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖应道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "韩宝驹一捋胡髭，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kang",
      "speaker_name": "杨康",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎认识我们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说着牵了两人坐骑去上料。杨康哼了一声，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖奇道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨康道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖更奇，问道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨康自知失言，脸上一红，强笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖点头道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这半夜里她到那里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大阿福",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖接口道：",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "让她多睡一会，且莫吵醒她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "另一个苍老的声音道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "靖哥哥，来捉我。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖点头道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖心下佩服，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "同仁老当",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那声音苍老的人道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "程大小姐道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她说的虽是江湖上的场面话，但神情腼腆，说一句话，便停顿片刻，一番话说来极是生疏，语言娇媚，说什么",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那老丐笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "清净散人",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黎生道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "程大小姐脸上一红。黎生又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "程大小姐道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黎生道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "程大小姐本来跃跃欲试，听黎生这么说了，不敢违拗，行了个礼，说道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "的笃、的笃、当当当",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "让丐帮的人先走。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "说",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公子爷，程家大小姐接来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "余兆兴叫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黎师叔，出来罢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黎生叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳克笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黎生说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳克仍满脸漫不在乎的神气，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黎生喝道：",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳克道：",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "黎生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他也会降龙十八掌！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉也点了点头，见黎生拳势沉重，少了",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "逍遥游",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "饭来伸手",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一招难挡。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "降龙十八掌",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "神龙摆尾",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "降龙廿八掌",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "履虎尾",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "神龙摆尾",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "转身拒敌。他武功远不及欧阳克精妙，拆了三四十招，已连遇五六次凶险，每次均仗这招",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "七公只传了他一掌。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "亢龙有悔",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "得有人大",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "且慢！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳克心想刚才这一掌不过碰巧，那将他放在心上，侧目斜视，笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳克笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "靖哥哥，揍这坏蛋！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉跃进厅来，笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳克摇头笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉大怒，反手一掌，喝道：",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "桃华落英掌",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "西毒",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "却不知郭靖本来不会此招，但见黎生反覆使了几次，拳理又与",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "神龙摆尾",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳克手上与郭靖对招，心中也暗暗称奇：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "见龙在田",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "亢龙有悔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他不知郭靖这三招其实全然无用，只是先前手腕受击，再也不敢冒进，渐渐放慢拳法，要以游斗耗他气力，忽然发觉郭靖有一掌的出手与上一次略有不同，心念一转：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "喝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鼠辈暗算公子爷，有种的光明正大出来⋯⋯",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "齐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "七公！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "同声说",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "帮主！您老人家好。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "躬身唱喏，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳克道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳克忙道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳克道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 594
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "洪七公道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳克道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "洪七公道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 610
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳克道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 610
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "转头说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 622
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "手一伸，已快如闪电的把欧阳克手中的摺扇抢了过来，一挥之下打开摺扇，见一面画着几朵牡丹，题款是",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 622
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "扇子一面写着几行字，下款署着",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 626,
      "line_end": 626
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这几个字写得怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳克向郭靖一指道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖摇头道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 644,
      "line_end": 644
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "靖儿，你是我徒弟么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 648,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "洪七公向欧阳克道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 650
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳克心中甚是奇怪：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 650
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖大喜，忙扑翻在地，磕了几个响头，口称：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 658
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "日前在归云庄上，他向六位师父详述洪七公传授",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "打一顿屁股。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 666,
      "line_end": 666
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "凝神看他传授郭靖掌法，但看他比划的招数，却觉平平无奇；又见洪七公在郭靖耳边低声说话，料是教导这三招的精义，郭靖思索良久，有时点点头，大半时候却总茫然摇头，要洪七公再说几遍，才勉强点头，显然也未必便当真领会了，心想：",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 672,
      "line_end": 672
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "降龙十八掌",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 682,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "靖儿，住手，咱们就算暂且输了这一阵。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 700,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "且慢，我有话说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 716,
      "line_end": 716
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "洪七公摇头笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 720,
      "line_end": 720
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉装作恍然大悟，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 722,
      "line_end": 722
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "洪七公让她一激，加之对她本就十分喜爱，脸孔一板，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 724,
      "line_end": 724
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "洪七公一时不明她用意，但知小姑娘鬼灵精，必有古怪，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 732,
      "line_end": 732
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 734,
      "line_end": 734
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "洪七公道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 734,
      "line_end": 734
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 736,
      "line_end": 736
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "洪七公道：",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 736,
      "line_end": 736
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉点点头，向洪七公霎了霎眼，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 738,
      "line_end": 738
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳克心想：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 748,
      "line_end": 748
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "笑了一笑，说道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 750,
      "line_end": 750
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳克道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 754,
      "line_end": 754
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉嫣然一笑，说道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 756,
      "line_end": 756
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "呼地一拳打出，正是洪七公所传的",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 758,
      "line_end": 758
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "桃华落英掌",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 760,
      "line_end": 760
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "灵蛇拳",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 766,
      "line_end": 766
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "灵蛇拳",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 770,
      "line_end": 770
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳克道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 776,
      "line_end": 776
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳克",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 776,
      "line_end": 776
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 794,
      "line_end": 794
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说着向欧阳克那些白衣姬妾一指，又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 796,
      "line_end": 796
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们是文打还是武打？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 808,
      "line_end": 808
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "问道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 810,
      "line_end": 810
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 810,
      "line_end": 810
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳克道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 814,
      "line_end": 814
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳克那能占她的先，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 818,
      "line_end": 818
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 820,
      "line_end": 820
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳克正想说：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 822,
      "line_end": 822
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只听得黄蓉叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 824,
      "line_end": 824
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两手钢针齐发，上下左右，无异一百余枚，那正是洪七公所授她的",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 830,
      "line_end": 830
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师父，干么救这坏家伙？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 844,
      "line_end": 844
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拍拍黄蓉的肩膀道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 848,
      "line_end": 848
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我可不要你的竹棒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 852,
      "line_end": 852
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
